quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Twaa Siin Miim
  26,2,Ebyo bye bigambo by'ekitabo ekinnyonnyola
  26,3,Olabika nga ayagala okwetta olw'okuba bagaanye okuba abakkiriza
  26,4,"Singa twagadde twandissizza ku bo okuva mu ggulu akabonero, ensingo zaabwe nezikugondera olubeerera"
  26,5,Tewali bubaka bwonna bupya kuva wa Katonda Omusaasizi ennyo wabula bo babuwakanya
  26,6,"Nebaba nga mazima balimbisa, bigenda kubajjira ebigambo ebyo bye baali bajeeja"
  26,7,Abaffe tebatunuulira nsi ne balaba bimeka bye twameza mu yo mu buli mutindo oguvaamu emigaso
  26,8,"Mazima mu ekyo ddala mulimu akabonero (akalaga obuyinza bwaffe), wabula bangi mu bo tebakkiriza"
  26,9,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi ennyo
  26,10,"Era jjukira ekiseera Mukama omulabiriziwo bwe yakoowoola Musa (naamulagira) nti: genda eri abantu abeeyisa obubi"
  26,11,Abantu ba Firaawo (obagambe nti) abaffe tebatya Katonda
  26,12,"(Musa) naagamba nti: mazima nze ntya okuba nga bannimbisa"
  26,13,"Ekifuba kyange ne kifunda olulimi lwange ne rutayatula, n'olwekyo lagira Haruna (annyambeko)"
  26,14,"Ate banninako omusango, ntya nti bayinza okunzita"
  26,15,(Katonda) naagamba nti nedda mugende n'obubonero bwaffe mazima ffe tuli wamu na mmwe tuwulira (tugoberera buli ekigenda mu maaso)
  26,16,Mugende ewa Firaawo mumugambe nti mazima ffe tutumiddwa Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,17,(Atugambye nti) tuwe abaana ba Israil tugende nabo
  26,18,"(Firaawo) naagamba nti tetwakukuliza mu ffe okuva nga oli mwana muto, era nga wawangaalira mu ffe emyaka mingi ku buwangaazibwo"
  26,19,Era nookola ekikolwakyo ekyo kye wakola e kyakufuula okuba mu batasiima bye bakolerwa
  26,20,(Musa) naagamba nti nnakikola bwe nnali nkyali mu babuze
  26,21,"Olwo nno nembadduka bwe nnabatya, awo Mukama omulabirizi wange nangabira okumanya e nsonga era nanteeka mu babaka"
  26,22,Ne'kyo e kyengera (eky'okundera n'okukulira mu mmwe) okindalaasaako naye nga ggwe abaana ba Israil wabafuula abaddu
  26,23,Firaawo naagamba nti Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna gwoyogerako yaani
  26,24,Musa naagamba nti Mukama omulabirizi w'eggulu omusanvu n'ensi n'ebiri wakati wa byombi bwe muba nga mwetegereza ebintu
  26,25,"(Firaawo) kwe kugamba abaali naye awo nti: abaffe temuwulira (nga bwabijweteka)"
  26,26,"(Musa) naagamba nti ye Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe, era Mukama omulabirizi wa bakadde ba mmwe abaasooka"
  26,27,"(Firaawo) naagamba nti: mazima omubaka wa mmwe oyo eyatumiddwa gye muli mulalu"
  26,28,(Musa) naagamba nti (ye) Mukama omulabirizi w'ebuvanjuba n'ebugwanjuba n'ebyo ebiri wakati wa byombi singa mubadde mutegeera
  26,29,(Firaawo) naagamba nti mazima singa oteekawo Katonda omulala atali nze nja kukuteera ddala mu b'okusibwa
  26,30,(Musa) naagamba nti ne bwennaaba nkuleetedde ekintu ekyeyolefu (ekiraga obutuufu bw'ebyo bye ngamba)
  26,31,(Firaawo) naagamba nti kale kireete bwoba nga oli mu boogera amazima
  26,32,"Awo nno Musa naasuula omuggogwe, okugenda okulaba nga musota omweyolefu"
  26,33,Era naggyayo omukonogwe okugenda okulaba nga ggwo gwakaayakanira abalabi
  26,34,(Firaawo) naagamba abo abaali batudde waali nti mazima ono mulogo kafulu
  26,35,Ayagala kubaggya mu nsi yammwe ku lw'eddogolye kati mugamba ki
  26,36,Ne bagamba nti mulagaanyise ne Mugandawe (ddi na wwa) aw'okubasisinkana era otume mu bitundu eby'enjawulo abakungaanya abalogo
  26,37,Bajja kukuleetera buli mulogo kakensa
  26,38,Olwo nno abalogo ne bakungaanyizibwa mu kiseera ekiragaane ku lunaku olumanyiddwa
  26,39,Abantu baagambibwa nti abaffe mmwe munajja
  26,40,Sikulwa nga tunaagoberera abalogo bwe banaaba bo nga be bawangudde
  26,41,Abalogo bwe bajja baagamba Firaawo nti mazima tuteekwa okuweebwa empeera bwe tunaaba nga ffe tuwangudde
  26,42,(Firaawo) naagamba nti weewaawo era mazima mmwe singa kinaaba bwe kityo mujja kubeera ba ku lusegere
  26,43,Musa naabagamba nti kale mwanje kye mwanja
  26,44,Nebasuula e miguwa gya bwe n'emiggo gya bwe era ne bagamba nti ku lw'ekitiibwa kya Firaawo mazima ffe tujja okuwangula
  26,45,Olwo nno Musa naasuula omuggogwe okugenda okulaba nga gwo gumira buli kye baali bagunjizzaawo
  26,46,Awo nno abalogo ne beeyala nga bavunnama
  26,47,Nebagamba nti tukkirizza Mukama Omulabirizi w'ebitonde
  26,48,Mukama omulabirizi wa Musa ne Haruna
  26,49,"Firaawo naagamba nti: mukkirizza byagamba nga sinnaba kubawa lukusa, (kirabika) nti mazima yye ye mukulu wa mmwe oyo eyabayigiriza eddogo, kale nno mujja kukitegeera, nja ku bakutulako e mikono gya mmwe n'amagulu ga mmwe nga bwe nkuggyako okugulu okwa ddyo, omukono nkuggyako gwa kkono, era ddala mwenna nja ku bakomerera ku musaalaba"
  26,50,"Ne bagamba nti ekyo tekiriimu buzibu, (anti) mazima ffe tujja kuba tudda eri Mukama omulabirizi waffe"
  26,51,Mazima ffe tululunkanira okuba nga Mukama omulabirizi waffe atusonyiwa ebyonoono byaffe bwe tuba nga ffe abakkiriza abasooka
  26,52,"Era netutumira Musa nti tambula ekiro n'abaddu bange, mazima mmwe mujja kulondoolwa"
  26,53,Firaawo naatuma mu bibuga abakungaanya (eggye era naagamba nti)
  26,54,Mazima abo kabiina ka bantu batono
  26,55,Era mazima bbo batunyiizizza
  26,56,Era nga bulijjo mazima ffe nga tukolera wamu tuli abantu abeekengera
  26,57,(Okusinziira ku nteekateeka zaabwe ne bye bakola ate) twabaggya mu malimiro ne nsulo ezikulukuta
  26,58,N'amawanika n'ebifo eby'ekitiibwa
  26,59,Bwe tutyo nno ne tubisikiza abaana ba Israil
  26,60,Olwo nno nebabagoberera nga busaasaana
  26,61,Ebibinja byombi bwe byalengeragana abantu ba Musa baagamba nti mazima ffe bajja kutukwata (batutte)
  26,62,(Musa) naagamba nti nedda mazima Mukama omulabirizi wange ali nange ajja kundaga eky'okukola
  26,63,"Awo nno ne tutumira Musa nti kuba omuggogwo ku nnyanja, olwo neebajjukamu, buli kibajjo ne kiba nga olusozi olunene"
  26,64,Netusembeza awo abalala (Firaawo ne ggyerye nabo ne bayingira e kkubo Musa lye yakuba ku nnyanja)
  26,65,Netuwonya Musa n'abaali naye bonna
  26,66,Oluvanyuma ne tuzikiriza abasigadde
  26,67,Mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebaali bakkiriza
  26,68,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi
  26,69,Era basomere ebigambo ebikwata ku Ibrahim
  26,70,Bwe yagamba kitaawe n'abantu be nti musinza biki
  26,71,Nebagamba nti tusinza amasanamu tubeera we gali era ne tugawa ebiseera bingi mu kugasinza
  26,72,(Ibrahim) naagamba nti abaffe bwe musaba gabawulira
  26,73,Oba gabagasa oba gasobola okubatuusaako akabi
  26,74,Nebagamba nti nedda wabula bwe tutyo bakadde baffe bye twasanga bakola
  26,75,Naagamba nti mulaba ebyo bye musinza
  26,76,Mmwe ne bakadde ba mmwe abaabakulembera
  26,77,"Mazima byo balabe bange, okugyako Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna"
  26,78,"Oyo eyantonda, yye y'annungamya"
  26,79,Era yye yooyo andiisa nannyweesa
  26,80,Era bwe ndwala yye y'amponya
  26,81,Era yooyo anzita ate nampa obulamu
  26,82,Era yye gwe ndulunkanira abe nga ansonyiwa ebyonoono byange ku lunaku lw'okusasulwa
  26,83,Ayi Mukama omulabirizi ngabira okumanya ensonga era onsisinkanye abalongoofu
  26,84,Era onteerewo okwogerwako obulungi mu balijja oluvanyuma
  26,85,Era onteeke mu balisikira e jjana ey'ebyengera
  26,86,Era sonyiwa Kitange mazima yye yali mu babuze
  26,87,Era tonswazanga olunaku lwe balizuukizibwa
  26,88,Olunaku emmaali n'abaana lwe bitaligasa
  26,89,Okugyako (aliganyulwa) yooyo alijja ewa Katonda n'omutima omuyonjo
  26,90,E jjana erisembezebwa eri abatya Katonda
  26,91,N'omuliro ne gulagibwa eri ababuze
  26,92,Era bagenda kugambibwa nti biriwa ebyo bye mwasinzanga
  26,93,"Ne muleka Katonda, abaffe bisobola okubataasa oba byo bisobola okwetaasa"
  26,94,Olwo nno ne bakasukibwa mu gwo bo n'ababuze
  26,95,Na bonna abali muggye lya Ibuliisu
  26,96,Baligamba nga bali mu gwo nga bakaayagana (nti)
  26,97,Tulayira Katonda nti mazima ddala twali mu bubuze obw'olwatu
  26,98,Bwe twabenkanya (mmwe) ne Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,99,Era tewali yatubuza okugyako aboonoonyi
  26,100,N'olwekyo tetulina bawolereza
  26,101,Wadde ow'omukwano alumirwa
  26,102,Naye singa tubadde tulina omukisa (okudda ku nsi) ne tuba mu bakkiriza
  26,103,Mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebakkiriza
  26,104,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaazizi
  26,105,Abantu ba Nuhu baalimbisa ababaka
  26,106,Mu kiseera muganda waabwe Nuhu we yabagambira nti abaffe temutya (Katonda)
  26,107,Mazima nze gye muli ndi mubaka omwesigwa
  26,108,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,109,"Era sikibasabirako mpeera, empeera yange teri okugyako ku Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna"
  26,110,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,111,Nebagamba nti abaffe tukukkirize nga abakugoberedde be ba wansi
  26,112,"Naagamba nti: mmanya ntya bye baali bakola"
  26,113,Okubalibwa kwa bwe tekuli okugyako kuli ku Mukama omulabirizi wange singa mubadde mumanyi
  26,114,Ate nze siri wa kugoba bakkiriza (olw'okuba ba wansi)
  26,115,Nze siri okugyako omutiisa ow'olwatu
  26,116,"Nebagamba nti: owange Nuhu bwo teekomeko ojja kubeerera ddala mu b'okukubwa amayinja"
  26,117,Naagamba nti ayi Mukama omulabirizi wange mazima abantu bange bannimbisizza
  26,118,"Kale salawo wakati wange nabo olusalawo olwannamaddala, era omponye owonye n'abakkiriza bendi nabo"
  26,119,Ne tumuwonya n'abo abaali naye mu lyato eryali lijjudde
  26,120,Oluvanyuma twazikiriza abaasigala
  26,121,Mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebakkiriza
  26,122,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi
  26,123,Abantu ba A’di baalimbisa ababaka
  26,124,Mu kiseera muganda waabwe Hudu lwe yabagamba nti abaffe temutya (Katonda)
  26,125,Mazima nze gye muli ndi mubaka omwesigwa
  26,126,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,127,Era sikibasabirako mpeera empeera yange teri okugyako ku Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,128,Abaffe muzimba ku buli katunnumba ekijjukizo nga muzannya buzannyi
  26,129,Era nemweteerawo amayumba amagundiivu nga mulinga abalibeerawo olubeerera
  26,130,Ate bwe mukwata (abalabe ba mmwe) mukwata enkwata eya ba kirimaanyi (abanyigiriza bannaabwe)
  26,131,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,132,Era mutye oyo abagabirira ebyo bye mumanyi
  26,133,Abagabirira ebisolo ebirundibwa era n'abaana
  26,134,N'amalimiro n'emigga
  26,135,Mazima nze ku lwa mmwe ntya ebibonerezo by'olunaku oluzibu
  26,136,Nebagamba nti kyekimu obuuliridde oba toli mu babuulirira
  26,137,Tekiri kino (eky'okubuulirira kwokola) okugyako nkola ya baasooka
  26,138,Era ffe tetuli ba kubonerezebwa
  26,139,"Nebamulimbisa olwo nno ne tubazikiriza, mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebakkiriza"
  26,140,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi
  26,141,Abantu ba Thamud baalimbisa ababaka
  26,142,Mu kiseera muganda waabwe Swalehe we yabagambira nti abaffe temutya (Katonda)
  26,143,Mazima nze gye muli ndi mubaka mwesigwa
  26,144,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,145,Era sikibasabirako mpeera empeera yange teri okugyako ku Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,146,(Mulowooza nti) mujja kulekebwa mirembe mu bintu ebiri wano
  26,147,(Nga muli) mu malimiro n'emigga
  26,148,N'ebimera n'emitende egiweese enkota enzito
  26,149,Era nemukola amayumba mu nsozi mu ngeri y'ekikugu
  26,150,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,151,Era temugondera ekigambo ky'abasukka e nsalosalo za Katonda
  26,152,Abo aboonoona mu nsi nebatalongoosa
  26,153,Nebagamba nti mazima ggwe oli wa mu baloge
  26,154,"Toli ggwe okugyako muntu nga ffe, kale leeta akabonero bwoba nga oli mu boogera amazima"
  26,155,"Naagamba nti engamiya yiino, erina okunywa (ku lunaku lwayo) nammwe munywe ku lunaku olumanyiddwa"
  26,156,Temugituusangako kabi ne bibakwata e bibonerezo by'olunaku oluzito
  26,157,Wabula baagifumita (neefa) olwo nno ne baba nga bejjusa
  26,158,"Ebibonerezo ne bibatuukako mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga, naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebakkiriza"
  26,159,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi
  26,160,Abantu ba Luutu baalimbisa ababaka
  26,161,Mu kiseera Muganda waabwe Luutu we yabagambira nti abaffe temutya (Katonda)
  26,162,Mazima nze gye muli ndi mubaka omwesigwa
  26,163,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,164,Era ssi kibasabirako mpeera empeera yange teri okugyako ku Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,165,Abaffe mu bitonde byonna ne mwagalamu basajja
  26,166,"Ne muleka ekyo Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe kye yabatondera mu abo be mwafumbiriganwa nabo, wabula mmwe muli bantu abasukka ebikomo"
  26,167,Nebagamba nti owange Luutu bwoteekomeko ojja kubeerera ddala mu bafulumizibwa (ne bagobwa mu nsi eno)
  26,168,Naagamba nti mazima ndi omu ku batamwa ekikolwa kya mmwe (eky'ebisiyaga)
  26,169,Ayi Mukama omulabirizi wange mponya n'abantu bange mu ebyo bye bakola
  26,170,Netumuwonya n'abantu be bonna
  26,171,Okugyako omukazi omukadde omu eyali mu baasigala
  26,172,Oluvanyuma twazikiriza abalala (bonna)
  26,173,"Netubatonnyesaako enkuba, mazima yali mbi nnyo enkuba y'abo abaalabulwa (ne bateebuulirira)"
  26,174,Mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga kinene naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebakkiriza
  26,175,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi
  26,176,Abantu b'o mu kitundu eky'ekibira baalimbisa ababaka
  26,177,Mu kiseera Swaibu bwe yabagamba nti abaffe temutya (Katonda)
  26,178,Mazima gye muli ndi Mubaka omwesigwa
  26,179,Kale mutye Katonda era mungondere
  26,180,Era sikibasabirako mpeera empeera yange teri okugyako ku Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,181,Era mutuukirizenga okupima temubeera mu abo abafiiriza abalala
  26,182,Mupimisenga ebipimo ebituufu
  26,183,"Temukendeerezanga abantu ebintu bya bwe, temukolanga ebibi mu nsi ne muba aboonoonyi"
  26,184,Era mutye oyo eyabatonda n'atonda n'emirembe egyasooka
  26,185,Nebagamba nti mazima ggwe oli mu baloge
  26,186,"Toli ggwe okugyako muntu nga ffe, era tukulowooza okuba nti oli mu balimba"
  26,187,Kale nno tusuuleko ekibajjo okuva waggulu bwoba nga oli mu boogera amazima
  26,188,Naagamba nti Mukama omulabirizi wange yaasinga okumanya ebyo bye mukola
  26,189,Wabula baamulimbisa ne bibakwata ebibonerezo ku lunaku ekire lwe kyabasiikiriza. Mazima kyo kyali kibonerezo kya lunaku oluzito
  26,190,Mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebakkiriza
  26,191,"Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo, ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi"
  26,192,Era mazima yyo (Kur’ani) yassibwa Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,193,Yakka nayo mwoyo omwesigwa (Jiburilu)
  26,194,(Naagissa) ku mutima gwo olyoke obe mu batiisa (abantu okukola ebibi)
  26,195,Nga eri mu lulimi oluwarabu olutegeerekeka
  26,196,Era mazima yo eyogerwako mu bitabo eby'edda ebyasooka
  26,197,Abaffe tekibamala kuba bujulizi okuba nti bagimanyi abayivu b'abaana ba Israil
  26,198,Singa twagissa ku bamu mu batali bawarabu
  26,199,Olwo nno (omu kubo) naagibasomera tebandigikkirizza
  26,200,Bwe kityo twagiyingiza mu mitima gy'aboonoonyi
  26,201,Tebagenda kugikkiriza okutuusa lwe baliraba ebibonerezo ebiruma
  26,202,Ebiribajjira ekibwatukira nga bo tebategedde
  26,203,Olwo nno bagambe nti abaffe tusobola okulindirizibwa
  26,204,Abaffe ebibonerezo byaffe bye basaba okubaleetera amangu
  26,205,Okiraba nti singa tubawangaazizza emyaka (egiwera)
  26,206,Oluvanyuma ne bibajjira ebyo bye balagaanyisibwa
  26,207,Tebiyinza kubayamba ebyo bye baaweebwa okweyagaliramu
  26,208,Tewali kitundu kye twazikiriza okugyako nga kimaze kufuna batiisa (ba Nabbi)
  26,209,"(Kyabanga bwe kityo) lwa kubabuulirira, tetubangako balyazaamaanyi"
  26,210,Era Sitane ssi ze zaajissa (Kur’ani)
  26,211,Era tekizisaanira era nga tezikisobola
  26,212,(Ku lw'ensonga nti) mazima zaaziyizibwa okuwulira ebifa mu ggulu
  26,213,(N'olwekyo) bwoba osinza Katonda tomugattako kintu kirala (anti bwokikola) obeera wa mu balibonerezebwa
  26,214,Era tiisa ab'oluganda lwo ab'okumpi
  26,215,Era kakkanya ekiwawaatiro kyo (weewombeke) eri oyo aba akugoberedde mu bakkiriza
  26,216,Wabula bwe bakujeemera gamba nti mazima nze nnesambye ebyo bye mukola
  26,217,Era weekwate ku nantakubwa ku mukono omusaasizi
  26,218,Oyo akulaba woobeerera nga oyimiridde (mu kusaala)
  26,219,Era n'alaba okwekyusakyusakwo mu bavunnama
  26,220,Mazima yye y'awulira ennyo omumanyi
  26,221,Abaffe mbategeeze Sitane zikka ku ani
  26,222,Zikka ku buli musazi w'abigambo omwonoonyi
  26,223,Abo abasaasaanya bye bawulira naye nga abasinga obungi mu bo balimba
  26,224,"Era abatontomi, ababuze be babagoberera"
  26,225,Abaffe tolaba nti babulubuutira mu buli lusenyi
  26,226,Era nti mazima bbo boogera bye batakola
  26,227,"Okugyako abo abakkiriza ne bakola emirimu emirungi ne boogera nnyo ku Katonda era ne baba nga beetaasa oluvanyuma lw'okuba nti bayisibwa bubi, era mazima abo abeeyisa obubi bagenda kumanya buddo ki gye balidda"